      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>cider vinegar </strong>and<strong> </strong>2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong> in a large bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>shredded red cabbage</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) to the bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>red cabbage slaw</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>chilli relish </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>chilli mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
