    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have softened, add the <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), 1 tsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tsp] </span><strong>black pepper</strong> and a large pinch of <strong>salt </strong>to the pan</p><p>Add another drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and stir until the mushrooms are coated in the spices</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min further or until fragrant – these are your <strong>Cajun-style mushrooms</strong></p>",
