    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, spread the <strong>warmed ciabatta</strong> with the <strong>chilli mayo</strong> and top with the <strong>Cajun-style mushrooms</strong> and some of the <strong>red cabbage slaw</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>slaw</strong> to the side and garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
